{
  "id": "kdenlive_4k60_multilayer_fx_render",
  "app": "kdenlive",
  "task": "Kdenlive is already open with the project file at /home/user/Documents/epic_4k.kdenlive (3840x2160, 60fps \u2014 4K UHD).\n\nImport six video clips from /home/user/Videos/: bg_wide.mp4, hero_a.mp4, hero_b.mp4, insert_1.mp4, insert_2.mp4, and credits.mp4. Set up the project with at least 8 tracks in total (video and audio combined). Arrange bg_wide.mp4 on Video Track 1 as a background layer spanning the full duration. Place hero_a.mp4 and hero_b.mp4 sequentially on Video Track 2 with a slight overlap, and add a Dissolve (`luma`) transition bridging that overlap. Place insert_1.mp4 on Video Track 3 so it overlaps in time with hero_a.mp4 on Track 2, and add a Composite and Transform (`qtblend`) transition between Track 2 and Track 3. Place insert_2.mp4 and credits.mp4 on Video Track 4. Apply the Edge Detection effect (`frei0r.sobel`) to the insert_1.mp4 clip, the Cartoon effect (`frei0r.cartoon`) to the hero_a.mp4 clip, the Glow effect (`frei0r.glow`) to the hero_b.mp4 clip, the Invert effect (`frei0r.invert0r`) to the insert_2.mp4 clip, and a Volume effect (`volume`) to any audio track. Save the project so the changes are persisted to /home/user/Documents/epic_4k.kdenlive, then render the project to /home/user/Documents/epic_4k_out.mp4 using the MP4 / H.264 preset. The project must remain at 3840x2160, 60fps.",
  "env": {
    "files": [
      {
        "filename": "epic_4k.kdenlive",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Documents/epic_4k.kdenlive"
      },
      {
        "filename": "bg_wide.mp4",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Videos/bg_wide.mp4"
      },
      {
        "filename": "hero_a.mp4",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Videos/hero_a.mp4"
      },
      {
        "filename": "hero_b.mp4",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Videos/hero_b.mp4"
      },
      {
        "filename": "insert_1.mp4",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Videos/insert_1.mp4"
      },
      {
        "filename": "insert_2.mp4",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Videos/insert_2.mp4"
      },
      {
        "filename": "credits.mp4",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Videos/credits.mp4"
      }
    ]
  },
